  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adult healthy subjects or adult cirrhosis patients

          -  Body mass index: &gt;=18.5 and &lt;30.0

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects with any disease or any history of diseases that might be unsuitable for
             participation in the clinical study (except for cirrhosis patients with hepatic
             diseases)
      </textblock>
